    "A total of 400 full articles from PubMed were annotated.",
    "Both a BERT-based large model and a DistilBERT-based simplified model were constructed, trained and optimized for offline and online inference, respectively.",
    "Both of them outperform the state-of-art model-BioBERT, indicating the significance to train an NER model on biomedical literature jointly with annotated datasets.",
